    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are an AI Department Classifier.\n\nYou will receive:\n- Task Title\n- Task Description\n\nTitle: {{ $('On form submission').item.json['Task Title'] }}\nDescription: {{ $('On form submission').item.json['Task Description'] }}\n\nYour job is to detect the correct department for this task.\n\nDepartment Rules:\n\nIT:\n- Technical problems\n- Bugs\n- Websites\n- Servers\n- Software\n- Login issues\n- Databases\n- AI systems\n\nHR:\n- Employee issues\n- Hiring\n- Leave requests\n- Attendance\n- Interviews\n- Payroll\n\nFinance:\n- Payments\n- Invoices\n- Salary\n- Taxes\n- Budgets\n- Fee issues\n\nMarketing:\n- Ads\n- Social media\n- Campaigns\n- Branding\n- Promotions\n- SEO\n\nSales:\n- Leads\n- Clients\n- Customer deals\n- Product selling\n- Outreach\n\nSupport:\n- Customer complaints\n- Helpdesk\n- User support\n- Troubleshooting\n\nOperations:\n- Internal management\n- Logistics\n- Workflow management\n- Scheduling\n\nGeneral:\n- If no clear department is found\n\nIMPORTANT:\nReturn ONLY one word from this list:\nIT\nHR\nFinance\nMarketing\nSales\nSupport\nOperations\nGeneral\n\nDo not add explanations.\nDo not add JSON.\nDo not add markdown.\nDo not add extra text.",
